    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. This example is equipped with the Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. Mechanically robust, the high-pressure VANOS system has been overhauled, and the rear subframe mounting points have been professionally reinforced to ensure chassis rigidity. Suspension remains tight with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers. While showing minor age-appropriate patina, the car exhibits linear power delivery and precise turn-in characteristics. Recent Blackstone oil analysis confirms rod bearing health. A mechanically sorted icon ready for the apex.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
