    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I'm parting ways with my reliable daily driver and it\u2019s looking for a great new home! It\u2019s been super well-loved and is still a total joy to drive. It's in really solid shape, runs beautifully, and is ready for your next big road trip or just the daily commute. It has a few minor signs of use as you'd expect, but it's been very well-maintained and feels great on the road. I'd love for you to come by, take it for a spin, and see for yourself how much fun it is! \u2728",
